.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^obs%^RESET%^ - the player to be busy with
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/events.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method allows creators to set the player for whom they are currently
busy too.
